OL,3,CStudents taking legal action against
OL,4,Cuni for suspending black history course
OL,6,FThe 14 students were all studying on
OL,7,Fthe Masters by Research (MRes),
OL,8,FHistory of Africa and the African
OL,9,FDiaspora course or conducting research
OL,10,Ffor a PhD at the University of
OL,11,FChichester when it made the decision
OL,12,Fto halt the programme for newcomers in
OL,13,FJuly 2023 because of the costs of
OL,14,Frunning the course.
OL,16,FThe university also made the course
OL,17,Fleader Professor Hakim Adi, the first
OL,18,FAfrican-British historian to become a
OL,19,Fprofessor of history in the UK and who
OL,20,Fwas shortlisted for the Wolfson
OL,21,FHistory Prize in 2023, redundant.
