OL,3,CStudents taking legal action against
OL,4,Cuni for suspending black history course
OL,6,FThe students have gone through the
OL,7,Funiversity's internal complaints
OL,8,Fprocedure "without resolution" for
OL,9,Ftheir claim that the departure of Prof
OL,10,FAdi has left them without adequate
OL,11,Fsupervision to complete their studies.
OL,13,FThey have now employed Leigh Day
OL,14,Fsolicitors to pursue a civil claim
OL,15,Falleging that the university is in
OL,16,Fbreach of contract and the firm issued
OL,17,Fa 'letter before action' on their
OL,18,Fbehalf on February 15.
