OL,3,CStudents taking legal action against
OL,4,Cuni for suspending black history course
OL,6,FLeigh Day partner Jacqueline McKenzie
OL,7,Fsaid: "This sudden decision by the
OL,8,FUniversity of Chichester to close down
OL,9,Fthis unique course has stopped our
OL,10,Fclients' academic careers in their
OL,11,Ftracks.
OL,13,F"On top of that, the university has
OL,14,Fmade an eminent and highly respected
OL,15,Fblack professor of African history in
OL,16,Fthe UK, who was last year nominated
OL,17,Ffor the Wolfson History prize,
OL,18,Fredundant at short notice.
