OL,3,CStudents taking legal action against
OL,4,Cuni for suspending black history course
OL,6,F"In our clients' view, the University
OL,7,Fof Chichester has clearly
OL,8,Fdiscriminated against them and
OL,9,Fbreached its contract with them in its
OL,10,Fhandling of this process.
OL,12,F"They are urging it to reverse this
OL,13,Fdecision and ensure sure that they can
OL,14,Fresume their studies as soon as
OL,15,Fpossible."
OL,17,FA university spokeswoman said that the
OL,18,Fclaims made on behalf of the students
OL,19,Fwere "inaccurate and misleading".
