OL,3,CStudents taking legal action against
OL,4,Cuni for suspending black history course
OL,6,FShe said: "For clarity, the MRes
OL,7,Fprogramme referred to has not been
OL,8,F'terminated' for existing students but
OL,9,Fis only suspended to new applicants
OL,10,Fpending a review.
OL,12,F"PhD students study individual
OL,13,Fprogrammes of research and should not
OL,14,Fbe conflated with the MRes programme.
OL,16,F"The university is committed to
OL,17,Fensuring that all existing students
OL,18,Fare able to complete their studies
OL,19,Fsuccessfully and that alternative
OL,20,Fteaching and supervisory arrangements
OL,21,Fare in place for these students."
